「等鏡頭過去了再告訴他」。他常說，食肉者是偽善的「食屍者」，最終都不適合選入優等民族。一個早期採用的納粹宣傳方式是出售香煙，香煙盒內附一張照片：熱愛自然的元首若有所思地削着蘋果。事實上，德國素食團體對希特拉在權力舞台的崛起幫助如此之大，他甚至一度考慮要在其政黨綱領中加入不食肉這個內容，只是當他又想到此舉會損害到食物供給體系和他所做的戰爭努力，這才作罷。當他終於在1933 年執政，素食運動的領袖們齊聲歡呼，擁戴他為救世主。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/K04NEL.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FK04NEL.html&d=LJrlrQnCPRTkRTA%2FSLTgpTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=91294df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/K04NEL.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:31:33.000Z","msg":"真正既環保素食撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 减少咗幾多碳排放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7dc1fc8bf16b53385977ffd670befe7bc06058","tid":681759,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53e2b3fa3b11d305958c551ddd35e827ae4e07ef","tid":681759,"uid":116471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c993e6d8e0cb9855e03f20f4b20912df955a8449","tid":681759,"uid":80481,"like":64,"dislike":6,"score":58,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"其實偽善有咩問題，如果一個人一生行善，即使佢心中有好多惡念，咁佢同真正既善人有咩分別呢，所以荀子先話其善者偽也"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"如果一生行惡，發動戰爭，但心中有好多善念呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:38:40.000Z","msg":"希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845dd5e9a1027e9b0fb5cf8a92f061d14dc58e86","tid":681759,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d781123b0f4ff0ba3e2c0b9eae72c8a1991b96","tid":681759,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d68a1c22a7cb70c4cba14e169496261a3bd4e6c","tid":681759,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike"